ed to, but she's still eating and drinking okay. Okay. And have you noticed any kind of weight changes at all recently? Has she lost any weight? No. No? Okay. and she had any loss of taste of smell or, sorry, loss of sense of taste or smell at all? No. Any muscle aches or anything like that? No, nothing like that. Okay. Any exposure to fumes, dust, or animals or pets at home? No, nothing like that. Okay. Any exposure to fumes, dust, or animals, or pets at home? No, nothing like that. Okay. And any... Has this happened at all in the past? No, not... No. No? Okay. No. Does she have any medical conditions at all that she's been diagnosed with in the past? Nope, nothing like that. Any, like, asthma or any other conditions? No. Okay. Any allergies that you know of? I know she has seasonal allergies, but that's about it. Okay. And does she take any medications at all on a daily basis? No, no. She just takes multivitamins. Okay. And currently, or previously, she had any surgeries or hospitalizations no no okay um are there any family history of uh any lung or heart conditions uh no any cancers there's some colon cancer on her dad's side of the family okay um there's some colon cancer on her dad's side of the family okay and is there any so do you remember who the person is and also like when they got diagnosed with the colon cancer so it was her uncle he was diagnosed when he was 45 okay um other than that uh were there any at all uh any developmental challenges at all while she was growing up? Was she meeting her milestones? Any concerns at all? No concerns. She was meeting all her milestones from what I remember. Okay. And in terms of her pregnancy, were there any, or your pregnancy with her, were there any complications at all, either during the pregnancy or after she was born um no no complications okay and uh right now uh where does she live and who does she live she lives at home with myself um a husband and she has um one younger sibling okay and is everyone at home