D: Okay, and anyone, anyone in your work environment, or uh in your home environment, or at school that has been sick around you?

P: Not that I've heard of, no. 

D: Okay. Um, and other than that, do you smoke at all?

P: Um, no I, well, I used to smoke before. I stopped last year.

D: Last year, okay. And how long did you smoke for?

